# A Tiny C++ class that uses AES algorithm to encrypt or decrypt data
# 一个小型的C++类，用于AES算法来加密/解密数据

It is a simple encapsulation of the [**tiny-AES-c**lib](https://github.com/kokke/tiny-AES-c), as detailed in the original library [https://github.com/kokke/tiny-AES-c](https://github.com/kokke/tiny-AES-c).

它是对[**tiny-AES-c**库](https://github.com/kokke/tiny-AES-c)的简单封装，原始库详见[https://github.com/kokke/tiny-AES-c](https://github.com/kokke/tiny-AES-c)。

Example：  
使用示例：  
```cpp
SimpleTinyAes simpleAes(SimpleTinyAes::AES_TYPE::AES256);

uint8_t key[] = { 0x60, 0x3d, 0xeb, 0x10, 0x15, 0xca, 0x71, 0xbe, 0x2b, 0x73, 0xae, 0xf0, 0x85, 0x7d, 0x77, 0x81,
                    0x1f, 0x35, 0x2c, 0x07, 0x3b, 0x61, 0x08, 0xd7, 0x2d, 0x98, 0x10, 0xa3, 0x09, 0x14, 0xdf, 0xf4 };
uint8_t in[]  = { 0xf3, 0xee, 0xd1, 0xbd, 0xb5, 0xd2, 0xa0, 0x3c, 0x06, 0x4b, 0x5a, 0x7e, 0x3d, 0xb1, 0x81, 0xf8 };
uint8_t out[]   = { 0x6b, 0xc1, 0xbe, 0xe2, 0x2e, 0x40, 0x9f, 0x96, 0xe9, 0x3d, 0x7e, 0x11, 0x73, 0x93, 0x17, 0x2a };
simpleAes.initCtx(key);
simpleAes.ecbDecrypt(in);
if (0 == memcmp((char*) out, (char*) in, 16)) {
    std::cout << "AES256 decrypt_ecb SUCCESS!"<< std::endl;
} else {
    std::cout << "AES256 decrypt_ecb FAILURE!"<< std::endl;
}
```

```cpp
SimpleTinyAes simpleAes(SimpleTinyAes::AES_TYPE::AES128);


uint8_t key[16] = { 0x2b, 0x7e, 0x15, 0x16, 0x28, 0xae, 0xd2, 0xa6, 0xab, 0xf7, 0x15, 0x88, 0x09, 0xcf, 0x4f, 0x3c };
uint8_t in[64]  = { 0x87, 0x4d, 0x61, 0x91, 0xb6, 0x20, 0xe3, 0x26, 0x1b, 0xef, 0x68, 0x64, 0x99, 0x0d, 0xb6, 0xce,
                    0x98, 0x06, 0xf6, 0x6b, 0x79, 0x70, 0xfd, 0xff, 0x86, 0x17, 0x18, 0x7b, 0xb9, 0xff, 0xfd, 0xff,
                    0x5a, 0xe4, 0xdf, 0x3e, 0xdb, 0xd5, 0xd3, 0x5e, 0x5b, 0x4f, 0x09, 0x02, 0x0d, 0xb0, 0x3e, 0xab,
                    0x1e, 0x03, 0x1d, 0xda, 0x2f, 0xbe, 0x03, 0xd1, 0x79, 0x21, 0x70, 0xa0, 0xf3, 0x00, 0x9c, 0xee };

uint8_t iv[16]  = { 0xf0, 0xf1, 0xf2, 0xf3, 0xf4, 0xf5, 0xf6, 0xf7, 0xf8, 0xf9, 0xfa, 0xfb, 0xfc, 0xfd, 0xfe, 0xff };
uint8_t out[64] = { 0x6b, 0xc1, 0xbe, 0xe2, 0x2e, 0x40, 0x9f, 0x96, 0xe9, 0x3d, 0x7e, 0x11, 0x73, 0x93, 0x17, 0x2a,
                    0xae, 0x2d, 0x8a, 0x57, 0x1e, 0x03, 0xac, 0x9c, 0x9e, 0xb7, 0x6f, 0xac, 0x45, 0xaf, 0x8e, 0x51,
                    0x30, 0xc8, 0x1c, 0x46, 0xa3, 0x5c, 0xe4, 0x11, 0xe5, 0xfb, 0xc1, 0x19, 0x1a, 0x0a, 0x52, 0xef,
                    0xf6, 0x9f, 0x24, 0x45, 0xdf, 0x4f, 0x9b, 0x17, 0xad, 0x2b, 0x41, 0x7b, 0xe6, 0x6c, 0x37, 0x10 };

simpleAes.initCtxIv(key, iv);
simpleAes.ctrXcryptBuffer(in, 64);
if (0 == memcmp((char*) out, (char*) in, 64)) {
    std::cout << "CTR AES128 SUCCESS!"<< std::endl;
} else {
    std::cout << "CTR AES128 FAILURE!"<< std::endl;
}
```

The above examples are also modified from the **tiny-AES-c** code repository.  
以上示例也均由**tiny-AES-c**代码库中内容修改而来。
